com.constantcontact.components.contacts

Class ContactList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.constantcontact.components.Component
      • com.constantcontact.components.contacts.ContactList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ContactList
extends Component
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a Contacts List for the Contact Service in Constant Contact.
    It may contain from one to many contacts.
    Doesn't actually store any contacts! BUT each Contact has an internal reference to the list(s) it is a member of.
    That "list of lists" can be retrieved using Contact.getLists()
    Author:
    ConstantContact
